<!doctype html>
<html lang="cs">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Třetí stránka</title>

  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #000000;
      font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace;
      font-size: 21px;
      letter-spacing: 0.13em;
    }

    main {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 36px 58px 24px;
    }

    .text {
      margin: 0 0 42px;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .text.second {
      margin-bottom: 96px;
    }

    .binary {
      margin: 0 0 24px;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      font-weight: normal;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .binary .bold {
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .arrows-code {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 19px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <main>
    <p class="text">
      Už je to tak dávno! Pořád to ale bolí jako dnes.<br>
      Pomstím se!
    </p>

    <p class="text second">
      Zabili jste ji. A já zabiju vás. Jsi poslední na<br>
      řadě.
    </p>

    <p class="binary">01000001 01001110 01001110 01000001
<span class="bold">00100000</span> 01000010 01011001 01001100
01000001 <span class="bold">00100000</span> 01001101 01001111 01001010
01000101 <span class="bold">00100000</span> 01000100 01000011
01000101 01010010 01000001 <span class="bold">00100001</span></p>

    <p class="arrows-code">1↑3↓2↓5↑0- 4↓3↑2↑2↓0- 3↑1↑5↓3↓0- 4↑6↑2↓4↓5↓0-</p>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
